  "title": "CONSTRUCTION SITE SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>The role is site-based, involving supervision of general construction tasks in indoor/outdoor conditions. The selected candidate will oversee the construction and repair of walls, partitions, arches, and other structures, ensuring all work is completed to project specifications. The candidate will also be responsible for maintaining safety and quality standards, managing a team of bricklayers, and coordinating with other site supervisors to ensure smooth operations.</p>",
